text: "Head over Feet" is a rock song from singer Alanis Morissette from Jagged Little Pill. The song talks of a couple who are best friends and lovers. It got positive reviews by critics. The song was released on 16 September 1996 in North America. It hit #1 on Billboard Adult Top 40. ==References== Category:1996 songs Category:Alanis Morissette songs Category:Rock songs
title: Head over Feet
